@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_llvckk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.90 / ((v2 + 0.09 + tmp + 0.04) * (v2 + 0.98 / v2 + 0.17)))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.73 * v2 + 0.04) - 0.77) + tmp)
    tmp = (v2 / wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.38 * v1 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
